```java
assertEquals("012", WordUtils.abbreviate("012 3456789", 2, 5, null));
```

Input: "012 3456789", lower=2, upper=5, append=null
- upper (5) is not less than lower (2), so no adjustment
- `index = StringUtils.indexOf("012 3456789", " ", 2)` = 3 (space at position 3)
